341
00:18:14,040 --> 00:18:15,020
 Ja se sjećam

342
00:18:15,020 --> 00:18:17,020
 tog ministarskog sastanka

343
00:18:17,020 --> 00:18:17,760
 kada je Ursula,

344
00:18:17,760 --> 00:18:19,440
 ova naša sada evropska,

345
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:20,540
 već kako šte ona,

346
00:18:20,540 --> 00:18:20,920
 ne znam,

347
00:18:20,920 --> 00:18:22,200
 ja to ne baš ne pratim,

348
00:18:22,200 --> 00:18:24,380
 si jela za storu

349
00:18:24,380 --> 00:18:24,720
 i rekla je

350
00:18:24,720 --> 00:18:25,140
 ne, ne, ne,

351
00:18:25,140 --> 00:18:26,060
 Njemačka neće zvajati

352
00:18:26,060 --> 00:18:27,720
 više od 1,1% za obranu.

353
00:18:27,740 --> 00:18:30,160
 8 godina poslije

354
00:18:30,160 --> 00:18:33,240
 se puno toga promijenilo.

355
00:18:33,240 --> 00:18:34,220
 E zašto?

356
00:18:34,220 --> 00:18:35,280
 Zato što je i ona bila

357
00:18:35,280 --> 00:18:36,600
 potpuno bez ikakvog iskustva,

358
00:18:36,600 --> 00:18:37,420
 zato što je ona bila

359
00:18:37,420 --> 00:18:38,600
 sljedbenica nečega,

360
00:18:38,600 --> 00:18:39,920
 zato što je i ona ta

361
00:18:39,920 --> 00:18:40,440
 koja je imala,

362
00:18:40,440 --> 00:18:41,440
 ne ona sama,

363
00:18:41,440 --> 00:18:42,360
 nego većina tih

364
00:18:42,360 --> 00:18:43,000
 evropskih plječara

365
00:18:43,000 --> 00:18:43,680
 nisu imali viziju

366
00:18:43,680 --> 00:18:44,200
 što se može

367
00:18:44,200 --> 00:18:45,200
 eventualno dogoditi,

368
00:18:45,200 --> 00:18:46,260
 pa su živjeli

369
00:18:46,260 --> 00:18:47,320
 po skutu nesadeja

370
00:18:47,320 --> 00:18:48,500
 od 45. godine,

371
00:18:48,500 --> 00:18:49,120
 nisu izdvajali

372
00:18:49,120 --> 00:18:49,560
 za obranu,

373
00:18:49,560 --> 00:18:50,160
 nisu izdvajali

374
00:18:50,160 --> 00:18:51,340
 za vlast u sigurnost

375
00:18:51,340 --> 00:18:53,160
 i sada se sve promijenilo.

376
00:18:53,160 --> 00:18:53,900
 E sad zamislimo

377
00:18:57,740 --> 00:18:58,140
 8 godina

378
00:18:58,140 --> 00:18:59,180
 ili nju sada.

379
00:18:59,180 --> 00:19:01,960
 To je velika razlika.

380
00:19:01,960 --> 00:19:02,840
 Stigde sam mi

381
00:19:02,840 --> 00:19:03,340
 mala država,

382
00:19:03,340 --> 00:19:04,000
 mala zemlja,

383
00:19:04,000 --> 00:19:05,200
 pa onda jednostavno

384
00:19:05,200 --> 00:19:06,240
 neke stvari

385
00:19:06,240 --> 00:19:07,400
 nemoguće promijeniti,

386
00:19:07,400 --> 00:19:07,780
 napravi,

387
00:19:07,780 --> 00:19:08,500
 mi ne ovisimo

388
00:19:08,500 --> 00:19:09,680
 sami o sebi,

389
00:19:09,680 --> 00:19:10,780
 mi ovisimo

390
00:19:10,780 --> 00:19:11,920
 o nekom drugom

391
00:19:11,920 --> 00:19:13,040
 i to je problem

392
00:19:13,040 --> 00:19:14,280
 i prokljestvo

393
00:19:14,280 --> 00:19:14,740
 i sudbina,

394
00:19:14,740 --> 00:19:15,400
 možda je sreća

395
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:16,080
 malih država.

396
00:19:16,080 --> 00:19:17,940
 Što nismo napeti

397
00:19:17,940 --> 00:19:18,320
 nekome,

398
00:19:18,320 --> 00:19:19,080
 pa se možemo

399
00:19:19,080 --> 00:19:19,600
 i sa strane,

400
00:19:19,600 --> 00:19:20,680
 ako smo pametni,

401
00:19:20,680 --> 00:19:22,180
 postavljati malo drugačije,

402
00:19:22,180 --> 00:19:22,820
 razvijati,

403
00:19:22,820 --> 00:19:24,100
 a samo ako imamo

404
00:19:24,100 --> 00:19:24,840
 narodno politikare,

405
00:19:24,920 --> 00:19:25,560
 koji imamo politikante,

406
00:19:25,560 --> 00:19:26,140
 nećemo nikad

407
00:19:26,140 --> 00:19:27,680
 zaći iz blata.

408
00:19:27,680 --> 00:19:29,200
 Ali mi imamo

409
00:19:29,200 --> 00:19:29,800
 političare

410
00:19:29,800 --> 00:19:31,160
 ili politikanti?

411
00:19:31,160 --> 00:19:32,140
 Imamo i ono,

412
00:19:32,140 --> 00:19:34,020
 puno malo,

